{
  "title": "Mildly Peppery Indian Potatoes Curry",
  "description": "A comforting and diabetic-friendly Indian dish featuring Jersey Royal potatoes in a mildly peppery lacquer-glaze, perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Indian",
