  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until it is lightly browned.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, turmeric, and cayenne pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the potatoes, salt, tomato puree, and water, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Use a potato masher to lightly mash some of the potatoes and thicken the sauce.",
    "Continue to simmer for an additional 10 minutes, or until the potatoes are tender.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the curry hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro if desired."
  ],
